Package org.project3.rest_api.models.wrappers

Class MenuItemWithQty

java.lang.Object
org.project3.rest_api.models.wrappers.MenuItemWithQty
public class MenuItemWithQty extends Object
The MenuItemWithQty class is a wrapper for MenuItem, associating a menu item with a specific quantity. This class is useful for tracking the quantity of a menu item in various contexts.
Author:
Kevin Zhang
